      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUST FAMOUS (5) tackled a Saturday race last start after a narrow defeat here as a $1.30 chance the start prior. He held his own in Saturday company and comes back to a race that looks to shape nicely for him. Should sit handy in the run and he can return to winning ways. SATURDAY SESH (9) is another who comes here on the back of some solid showings in Saturday company. The figures he's running in defeat there stack up in this field and he has enough class to negotiate the tricky barrier. Racing well without winning and finds his race today. THE SHOWVINIST (7) stepped up in distance last start and was just plain, though his run here two back was superb. Can mix his form but his best is good enough to feature in this event. PRAWNS ELEVEN (1) gets the blinkers on for the first time today and can't be left out of calculations back in distance. SURE THING (6) is next best.",
